Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.26,0:02:06.48,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}想试着谈场猜谜般的恋爱吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.48,0:02:09.02,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}星星在呢喃着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.15,0:02:11.94,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}虽然害怕…但还是想！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.44,0:02:17.40,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}光是安稳度日 也太无趣了点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.57,0:02:22.16,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}真希望能改变些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.16,0:02:25.87,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}既然想要个契机
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.04,0:02:27.54,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}那就飞奔出去吧 Boooon!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.54,0:02:31.71,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}回忆在骚动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.71,0:02:37.30,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}我…好像认识你！？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.67,0:02:41.43,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}不论是晴天雨天还是在下雪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.43,0:02:44.18,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}我都好想好想去见你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.39,0:02:45.60,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}从过去到未来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.72,0:02:46.85,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}从明天到未来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.02,0:02:49.73,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}是啊 时间 Nonstop
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.94,0:02:55.53,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}先前烦恼的事情 通通都消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.69,0:03:01.41,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}来展开新的故事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.57,0:03:06.49,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}又在做梦吗？现在的梦还不能说！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.00,0:03:09.33,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}大晴天也好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.83,0:03:12.00,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}下雨天也好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.17,0:03:17.09,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}不管是怎样的天气 I need you!!
